{"type": "article", "id": 15369, "title": "《高盛帝国》", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230749paKiTBvlURcszrdL.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.amazon.cn/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E5%B8%9D%E5%9B%BD-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E7%99%BE%E5%B9%B4%E5%B1%B9%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%BC%A0%E8%AE%B0-%E6%9F%A5%E5%B0%94%E6%96%AF%E2%80%A2%E5%9F%83%E5%88%A9%E6%96%AF/dp/B00PI1FYHU/ref=sr_1_2?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1442971538&amp;sr=1-2&amp;keywords=%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E5%B8%9D%E5%9B%BD\" target=\"_blank\">《高盛帝国》</a>，查尔斯•埃利斯<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t相比之下，研究者写的书大多就要逊色一点，更适合当资料来学习。Charles Ellis 的《高盛帝国》写得虽然面面俱到，对每个重要人物也都如数家珍，但在细节上就明显缺点底气。作者是<span>为高盛提供战略咨询服务超过 30 年的专家。简单来说，这本书说的是哪些人、哪些事成就了最辉煌时期的高盛。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}